WEBVTT

01:50.000 --> 01:53.900
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.250 --> 01:56.770
[Episode 9]

01:57.430 --> 01:59.430
I might not know how his career is going,

01:59.430 --> 02:00.480
but his character

02:00.480 --> 02:01.790
leaves much to be desired.

02:01.790 --> 02:04.200
He doesn't even know basic courtesy.

02:04.630 --> 02:06.740
He won't follow Rongcheng's rules.

02:07.560 --> 02:08.680
I'd better not run into him again,

02:08.680 --> 02:09.870
or I won't be able to stop myself
from lashing out,

02:09.870 --> 02:11.800
and everyone will be embarrassed.

02:12.120 --> 02:12.750
Alright.

02:15.400 --> 02:16.070
What?

02:17.600 --> 02:19.130
I won't let you run into him.

02:24.710 --> 02:25.940
Try this candied fruit.

02:25.940 --> 02:26.890
It's delicious.

02:44.370 --> 02:45.900
I picked it up along the way.

02:46.829 --> 02:48.670
I can no longer accept your gifts,

02:48.670 --> 02:50.320
even if you mean well.

02:50.320 --> 02:51.150
I'm not being kind.

02:51.150 --> 02:52.200
I'm seducing you.

02:52.550 --> 02:54.200
I give expecting something in return,

02:54.200 --> 02:55.530
and I make sure to get it.

02:55.980 --> 02:58.260
I won't marry you just because of a hat.

02:58.280 --> 02:59.380
Don't get ahead of yourself.

02:59.380 --> 03:00.470
I will not marry.

03:01.650 --> 03:03.460
Then I won't kiss you either.

03:14.040 --> 03:16.640
I almost forgot about
the real matters at hand.

03:17.079 --> 03:18.610
No, I don't want to kiss you,

03:19.000 --> 03:20.530
even though you may need it.

03:20.670 --> 03:21.800
That is the problem.

03:21.970 --> 03:23.180
You need someone

03:23.210 --> 03:24.410
who knows how to kiss.

03:24.920 --> 03:27.050
Then, do you think you're that person?

03:27.270 --> 03:29.590
She's not at

03:29.990 --> 03:31.120
the casino or hotel.

03:31.710 --> 03:32.960
Where else can she be?

03:33.340 --> 03:34.740
Are you an NPC or a player?

03:35.150 --> 03:36.610
Watch where you're going!

03:36.670 --> 03:37.400
Keep staring

03:37.640 --> 03:39.770
and I'll file a complaint against you!

04:02.520 --> 04:03.550
What's wrong?

04:04.390 --> 04:06.050
Is there something on my face?

04:07.110 --> 04:08.040
Wipe your mouth.

04:13.670 --> 04:15.550
There's a quality control issue with
the hawthorn balls

04:15.550 --> 04:16.790
from your store!

04:17.709 --> 04:19.760
It's the first time I've had customers
come for a murder mystery game,

04:19.760 --> 04:21.959
but complain about the hawthorn balls.

04:31.030 --> 04:31.760
Don't panic.

04:36.470 --> 04:37.120
Let's go.

04:42.960 --> 04:44.960
Chief Ning has lost important evidence.

04:44.960 --> 04:46.760
Everyone must be searched.

04:46.760 --> 04:48.760
Why are you hiding from Ning Zechen?

04:49.470 --> 04:50.120
Follow me.

04:51.960 --> 04:52.690
Hand it over.

05:00.640 --> 05:02.170
There's another exit here?

05:06.390 --> 05:06.960
This way.

05:09.270 --> 05:10.790
Where does this path lead?

05:11.680 --> 05:12.610
To the main hall.

05:12.790 --> 05:14.250
It's one of the fire exits.

05:14.790 --> 05:15.470
Let's go.

05:24.560 --> 05:25.520
General Qin.

05:29.350 --> 05:31.080
I'm going to find my friend now.

05:31.560 --> 05:33.680
I'll need to prepare for
the mayor's election too.

05:33.680 --> 05:35.000
Well then, General Qin,

05:35.000 --> 05:35.909
farewell.

05:37.200 --> 05:37.730
Alright.

05:40.760 --> 05:41.290
General!

05:42.470 --> 05:43.200
It's no good.

05:43.320 --> 05:44.680
The pocket watch you left in your office

05:44.680 --> 05:45.340
is missing.

05:46.120 --> 05:47.050
I took it with me.

05:47.590 --> 05:48.790
The watch is with you?

05:49.220 --> 05:50.350
Then I can rest easy.

05:51.760 --> 05:52.640
However,

05:53.320 --> 05:55.120
it shouldn't be with me anymore.

06:03.120 --> 06:03.790
This is...

06:03.950 --> 06:05.790
evidence of Ning Zechen's smuggling.

06:05.790 --> 06:06.320
General,

06:06.830 --> 06:08.360
where did you get this from?

06:18.850 --> 06:23.150
♪ Under the streetlight,
I grow increasingly weary ♪

06:24.940 --> 06:29.780
♪ A few specks of dust
drift by in the wind ♪

06:32.060 --> 06:36.220
♪ The girl who once
basked in the sunlight ♪

06:32.200 --> 06:32.790
Hu Xiu.

06:35.200 --> 06:36.200
General Qin,

06:36.440 --> 06:37.350
is there anything else?

06:36.900 --> 06:39.820
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

06:40.260 --> 06:43.240
♪ I don't understand either ♪

06:41.230 --> 06:42.030
Reporter Han,

06:42.760 --> 06:44.020
why are you helping me?

06:44.640 --> 06:46.590
When I first became a reporter,

06:45.470 --> 06:49.300
♪ Flicking through old chat logs ♪

06:47.680 --> 06:49.760
everyone thought I was naive

06:49.880 --> 06:51.210
and easy to manipulate.

06:51.550 --> 06:56.440
♪ I just realized the replies
were somewhat delayed ♪

06:52.200 --> 06:53.790
But I have my own beliefs.

06:55.080 --> 06:56.030
I believe in

06:56.200 --> 06:57.080
my dreams.

06:57.580 --> 07:03.570
♪ At the crossroads of choices,
amidst the bustling crowd ♪

06:57.830 --> 06:59.290
I believe in my intuition.

07:00.350 --> 07:01.560
And I believe...

07:04.800 --> 07:12.070
♪ Who hasn't paid the price
and still fallen short? ♪

07:06.640 --> 07:07.470
My intuition told me that

07:07.470 --> 07:08.830
General Qin will win.

07:10.350 --> 07:12.080
I will not betray my instincts,

07:12.090 --> 07:16.640
♪ Stand with me tonight,
look at the starlight ♪

07:13.120 --> 07:15.050
nor will I betray you, General Qin.

07:17.840 --> 07:23.880
♪ Even if we're always
pushed aside by reality ♪

07:18.680 --> 07:19.590
All the best.

07:24.690 --> 07:30.900
♪ I know the dark clouds will still come ♪

07:31.430 --> 07:37.780
♪ But in this world,
there will always be someone ♪

07:36.350 --> 07:38.970
[Character Background: As a rookie reporter, you were seen as naive and easily manipulated.
Yet you held fast to your dreams, your intuition, and your belief in truth and justice.]

07:38.990 --> 07:41.100
[Main Quest: First, make contact with Ning Zechen to receive specific instructions.
Then, posing as a journalist, arrange a meeting with Qin Xiao to find a breakthrough.]

07:39.790 --> 07:40.960
This line in the script...

07:40.510 --> 07:43.790
♪ Who looks forward
with the same hope as me ♪

07:42.000 --> 07:42.880
is so cool!

07:48.590 --> 07:49.560
Right foot.

07:55.680 --> 07:57.640
Where did Mr. Qian go?

07:58.200 --> 07:59.600
He's been gone for hours.

08:00.350 --> 08:01.680
Should I go look for him?

08:03.030 --> 08:03.680
Forget it.

08:03.680 --> 08:05.140
When he's done having fun,

08:05.150 --> 08:06.760
he'll show up naturally.

08:09.270 --> 08:09.780
Look,

08:10.470 --> 08:11.590
there he is.

08:14.880 --> 08:15.530
Let's go.

08:20.640 --> 08:21.270
Mr. Qian,

08:25.320 --> 08:26.450
where have you been?

08:26.470 --> 08:28.400
I've been looking all over for you.

08:28.520 --> 08:29.710
Don't even mention it.

08:29.710 --> 08:30.590
Mr. Guangming,

08:31.270 --> 08:32.559
before I came here, I heard that

08:32.559 --> 08:34.470
the NPCs here are all very good-looking.

08:34.470 --> 08:36.400
Lots of women spend money on them.

08:37.230 --> 08:38.679
But I never expected

08:38.870 --> 08:40.400
Ms. Hu is also such a person.

08:44.470 --> 08:46.670
Could there be some misunderstanding?

08:47.320 --> 08:48.790
There's no misunderstanding.

08:48.790 --> 08:50.390
She went shopping with me today.

08:50.390 --> 08:52.890
At first, she even complimented
how handsome I looked in my suit.

08:52.890 --> 08:54.990
Then suddenly, she was flirting
with someone else.

08:54.990 --> 08:55.750
She's just a woman

08:55.750 --> 08:58.150
who only cares about looks, not character.

08:58.350 --> 08:59.680
I really misjudged her.

09:01.630 --> 09:03.040
So shouldn't someone with neither looks

09:03.040 --> 09:04.320
nor character

09:04.320 --> 09:05.630
watch what they say,

09:05.630 --> 09:06.440
Mr. Qian?

09:06.630 --> 09:08.040
What do you mean by that?

09:08.350 --> 09:10.800
It's your friend who has
questionable character.

09:10.800 --> 09:11.960
I saw it with my own eyes.

09:11.960 --> 09:13.560
She was flirting and even getting physical

09:13.560 --> 09:14.230
with other male actors.

09:14.230 --> 09:14.590
Calm down.

09:14.590 --> 09:16.510
Watch your mouth!

09:17.160 --> 09:18.470
Why are you so upset?

09:18.920 --> 09:20.040
Don't tell me you already knew

09:20.040 --> 09:21.710
your friend was flirting with
other male actors.

09:21.710 --> 09:22.680
I dare you to say that again!

09:22.680 --> 09:23.960
And so what if I do?

09:25.590 --> 09:26.200
Mr. Qian.

09:26.410 --> 09:27.400
If you don't want to play this game,

09:27.400 --> 09:28.160
you can leave first.

09:28.160 --> 09:29.490
We can meet another day.

09:29.530 --> 09:30.460
Wang Guangming,

09:30.750 --> 09:32.800
Your wife and Hu Xiu
are the same kind of people.

09:32.800 --> 09:33.440
What decent girl

09:33.440 --> 09:35.710
would waste her money
in a place like this?

09:35.710 --> 09:36.510
What a scum!

09:37.990 --> 09:38.510
Enough.

09:38.510 --> 09:39.230
What a scum!

09:39.230 --> 09:40.290
Enough. Calm down.

09:40.630 --> 09:41.280
Calm down.

09:41.590 --> 09:42.680
Stop recording, will you?

09:42.680 --> 09:44.040
Stop recording.

09:44.040 --> 09:46.170
Where did a scumbag like you come from?

09:54.390 --> 09:54.780
I...

09:55.460 --> 09:56.350
Let go!

10:00.160 --> 10:01.040
Watch out!

10:02.630 --> 10:03.510
Danger!

10:12.490 --> 10:16.440
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

10:16.610 --> 10:20.340
♪ The motionless night began to shimmer ♪

10:18.040 --> 10:18.770
Are you okay?

10:19.710 --> 10:20.350
Xiu, are you okay?

10:20.350 --> 10:20.960
Come on.

10:20.750 --> 10:25.030
♪ The fireworks bear witness, as if ♪

10:21.630 --> 10:22.890
Mr. Xiao, your hand...

10:23.710 --> 10:24.320
It's fine.

10:24.320 --> 10:25.040
It's fine, really.

10:25.040 --> 10:26.160
How's your hand?

10:25.360 --> 10:28.590
♪ they're waiting for the words
we want to say ♪

10:27.920 --> 10:28.710
I'm the one who got hit.

10:28.710 --> 10:29.280
Why are you panicking?

10:29.050 --> 10:32.340
♪ I moved closer to you,
and you moved closer to me ♪

10:29.280 --> 10:30.320
How are you feeling?

10:30.320 --> 10:31.650
Are your bones alright?

10:33.200 --> 10:34.110
You...

10:33.550 --> 10:38.840
♪ It felt as if two lonely islands
had finally ♪

10:34.110 --> 10:34.710
try gripping my hand.

10:34.710 --> 10:36.040
Can you apply pressure?

10:39.480 --> 10:44.090
♪ Getting closer and slipped into
the flow of time together ♪

10:41.230 --> 10:42.400
I'm okay.

10:42.800 --> 10:45.060
You're messing up my gaming experience!

10:45.590 --> 10:45.960
I'm sorry.

10:45.960 --> 10:46.350
I can't continue anymore.

10:46.350 --> 10:47.880
Give us an explanation now!

10:50.440 --> 10:51.400
Don't touch me!

10:51.400 --> 10:52.320
What should we do?

10:52.320 --> 10:52.710
Let's call the police.

10:52.710 --> 10:53.560
All's good now.

10:53.560 --> 10:54.800
Why call the police?

10:55.160 --> 10:55.990
If this gets out,

10:55.990 --> 10:58.080
it won't look good for our club.

10:58.080 --> 11:00.080
Arrange full refunds for this session.

11:00.080 --> 11:01.280
Take down everyone's information.

11:01.280 --> 11:03.480
Everyone gets 30% off their next visit.

11:03.560 --> 11:06.870
Do you... have the authority
to make that decision?

11:07.040 --> 11:08.160
In my opinion,

11:08.160 --> 11:09.350
we should contact our boss first.

11:09.350 --> 11:10.280
Yes, yes.

11:10.280 --> 11:10.800
Let's contact our boss.

11:10.800 --> 11:11.800
I am the boss.

11:21.800 --> 11:22.830
How is your face?

11:22.830 --> 11:23.890
Does it still hurt?

11:24.080 --> 11:25.160
It's fine.

11:26.040 --> 11:27.440
You'd definitely slapped him back harder

11:27.440 --> 11:28.770
than what I had endured.

11:29.590 --> 11:30.750
It's his mouth.

11:30.750 --> 11:31.400
He can say

11:31.400 --> 11:32.280
whatever he wants.

11:32.280 --> 11:33.630
But I couldn't stand it.

11:34.110 --> 11:35.560
He was being so rude.

11:37.320 --> 11:38.630
Is that Qin Xiaoyi

11:38.660 --> 11:40.260
really the boss of this shop?

11:41.320 --> 11:42.160
If...

11:42.350 --> 11:43.320
he says so himself,

11:43.320 --> 11:44.800
then he must be.

11:44.900 --> 11:47.560
He keeps a much lower profile than
Gong Huaicong.

11:47.560 --> 11:48.800
You should go check on him quickly.

11:48.800 --> 11:51.060
I think he's in much worse shape
than I am.

11:51.160 --> 11:51.870
But...

11:52.230 --> 11:53.630
No buts.

11:53.630 --> 11:55.050
Wang is here with me.

11:55.070 --> 11:56.330
He will take care of me.

11:57.110 --> 11:58.320
Use this to ice it first.

11:58.320 --> 12:00.230
We'll use an ice pack when we get home.

12:00.230 --> 12:00.750
I'm sorry

12:00.750 --> 12:02.200
for causing you trouble today.

12:02.200 --> 12:03.200
I'm fine.

12:03.200 --> 12:04.400
I'll go check on Xiao—

12:05.160 --> 12:06.210
Qin Xiaoyi.

12:09.870 --> 12:12.640
All the players for this session
have been refunded.

12:12.640 --> 12:13.410
Wait.

12:13.480 --> 12:14.700
I can't believe I wasn't there

12:14.700 --> 12:16.230
for such a dramatic moment.

12:19.630 --> 12:21.080
I have to go now. Bye.

12:23.230 --> 12:24.400
You were waiting for me?

12:24.400 --> 12:26.200
I'll go to the hospital with you.

12:28.710 --> 12:29.830
You must get checked out.

12:29.830 --> 12:31.360
What if something's wrong?

12:32.390 --> 12:33.920
I didn't say I wasn't going.

12:34.230 --> 12:36.760
Architects don't mess around with
their own hands.

12:36.760 --> 12:38.220
Good that you understand.

12:38.630 --> 12:39.680
Let's go.

12:45.770 --> 12:46.430
[Emergency]

12:49.830 --> 12:50.560
We're here.

12:59.080 --> 12:59.610
Let's go.

13:00.590 --> 13:01.710
Alright.

13:01.850 --> 13:02.850
I hurt my arm,

13:02.880 --> 13:03.710
not my leg.

13:03.750 --> 13:05.280
I can still walk.

13:06.630 --> 13:07.890
Let's register first.

13:08.350 --> 13:08.830
Hello.

13:08.830 --> 13:10.280
My friend hurt his arm.

13:10.280 --> 13:11.230
How do we get to the clinic?

13:11.230 --> 13:12.160
Register first.

13:15.160 --> 13:15.920
Doctor.

13:15.920 --> 13:17.110
My friend injured his hand.

13:17.110 --> 13:17.730
I need to register.

13:17.730 --> 13:19.190
10 yuan for registration.

13:23.440 --> 13:24.440
Here's your card.

13:24.800 --> 13:25.330
Let's go.

13:28.950 --> 13:30.080
Can you bend it here?

13:31.110 --> 13:32.560
Gently, please!

13:35.250 --> 13:37.340
Your girlfriend seems quite concerned
about you.

13:37.340 --> 13:39.140
She's crying out in pain for you.

13:39.400 --> 13:40.400
Doctor, you misunderstood.

13:40.400 --> 13:40.800
I...

13:40.800 --> 13:41.990
We're not together.

13:42.240 --> 13:43.670
Doctor, is it serious?

13:44.990 --> 13:45.720
I'm not sure.

13:45.720 --> 13:47.180
Let's take an X-ray first.

13:48.110 --> 13:48.710
Oh, X-ray.

13:49.340 --> 13:50.080
Take him there first.

13:50.080 --> 13:51.060
It's on the second floor, right?

13:51.060 --> 13:51.650
Let's go.

13:51.670 --> 13:52.270
Thank you.

13:58.590 --> 14:00.630
Doctor, what's the diagnosis?

14:03.590 --> 14:04.750
I-Is it serious?

14:06.910 --> 14:07.840
The bone is fine.

14:07.870 --> 14:10.230
There's soft tissue contusion
with bruising.

14:10.230 --> 14:10.990
That's why

14:10.990 --> 14:11.920
this area

14:11.920 --> 14:12.990
is swollen.

14:14.110 --> 14:15.240
So what should we do?

14:15.510 --> 14:16.320
It's not serious.

14:16.320 --> 14:18.050
I'll prescribe some medicine.

14:18.400 --> 14:19.000
Remember,

14:19.400 --> 14:21.680
absolutely no spicy food or seafood.

14:21.680 --> 14:22.560
And this hand,

14:22.590 --> 14:23.850
don't strain it and keep movement minimal.

14:23.850 --> 14:24.790
Thank you, doctor.

14:24.790 --> 14:25.720
You're welcome.

14:45.160 --> 14:45.800
Let me see.

14:47.800 --> 14:48.800
It's much better.

14:51.440 --> 14:52.800
Did that project fall through?

14:52.800 --> 14:54.110
Don't mention the project.

14:54.110 --> 14:55.590
Who would work with someone like that?

14:55.590 --> 14:57.120
He'll fail sooner or later.

14:57.370 --> 14:58.100
That's true.

14:58.260 --> 14:59.920
Consider it dodging a bullet.

15:02.440 --> 15:03.080
Let's eat.

15:06.320 --> 15:07.080
Let's go.

15:12.510 --> 15:13.110
How is it?

15:13.110 --> 15:14.770
These are all your favorites.

15:15.990 --> 15:16.590
It's good.

15:16.960 --> 15:17.590
It's good?

15:30.040 --> 15:30.840
What's wrong?

15:33.160 --> 15:35.890
Mr. Qu wants me to attend
a technical conference.

15:36.560 --> 15:37.510
Is it far?

15:37.830 --> 15:38.710
Jinshan.

15:40.050 --> 15:41.170
That's not too bad.

15:41.190 --> 15:42.990
At least it's still in Shanghai.

15:49.350 --> 15:50.110
Let's eat.

15:55.200 --> 15:55.800
By the way,

15:56.230 --> 15:56.920
tomorrow,

15:57.000 --> 15:58.390
remember to transfer

15:58.470 --> 16:00.200
the medical expenses to Hu Xiu.

16:00.990 --> 16:01.750
I'll ask her tomorrow.

16:01.750 --> 16:03.210
She must be quite busy now.

16:08.320 --> 16:10.320
The dosage and instructions are
clearly stated on the labels.

16:10.320 --> 16:11.440
Make sure to take them on time.

16:11.440 --> 16:13.040
Call me if you need anything.

16:13.080 --> 16:13.990
Get down first.

16:13.990 --> 16:15.440
I'll go park the car.

16:15.990 --> 16:16.920
You've been busy all night.

16:16.920 --> 16:17.980
Aren't you hungry?

16:18.870 --> 16:20.200
I... I'm fine.

16:27.110 --> 16:27.800
I'm hungry.

16:29.300 --> 16:30.360
Let's go upstairs.

16:44.390 --> 16:45.060
Mr. Xiao,

16:45.280 --> 16:47.230
my cooking skills aren't that great.

16:47.230 --> 16:49.560
You're still better than me with one hand.

16:50.160 --> 16:50.710
Well then,

16:50.710 --> 16:52.170
what would you like to eat?

16:52.440 --> 16:53.520
Check the fridge

16:53.550 --> 16:54.750
and see what's there.

17:04.359 --> 17:05.359
What's this?

17:06.310 --> 17:08.569
I don't like taking advantage of others.

17:09.440 --> 17:10.510
So over here, you're figuring out

17:10.510 --> 17:12.160
how to keep live crabs fresh?

17:12.710 --> 17:13.680
At least for now,

17:13.680 --> 17:15.020
they seem to be holding up pretty well.

17:15.020 --> 17:16.020
Are they alive?

17:21.480 --> 17:22.160
It might still be alive,

17:22.160 --> 17:24.089
but you nearly smashed it to death.

17:35.100 --> 17:36.230
By the way, Mr. Xiao,

17:36.360 --> 17:38.510
you already got evidence of
Ning Zechen's smuggling.

17:38.510 --> 17:39.360
So why didn't you

17:39.360 --> 17:41.160
go straight to the mayor for
a command token

17:41.160 --> 17:42.660
and then enter the election?

17:42.660 --> 17:44.590
Why come to the dance hall instead?

17:49.840 --> 17:51.900
I was planning to give you this watch.

17:53.550 --> 17:54.400
You trusted me

17:54.750 --> 17:56.330
and gave me the smuggling evidence.

17:56.330 --> 17:57.510
So of course, I should give you
something in return

17:57.510 --> 17:58.840
to put your mind at ease.

17:59.090 --> 18:01.550
That's what mutual trust is about,
isn't it?

18:03.440 --> 18:05.550
You're so smooth-talking now.

18:05.550 --> 18:07.010
Where was all this before?

18:14.270 --> 18:15.870
On that day of the site visit,

18:15.880 --> 18:17.550
it wasn't that I didn't trust you.

18:17.550 --> 18:18.880
I didn't trust Zhuling.

18:19.400 --> 18:20.710
I have no idea what they might do

18:20.710 --> 18:22.040
to achieve their goals.

18:25.200 --> 18:26.120
So...

18:26.750 --> 18:28.230
you weren't being suspicious,

18:28.230 --> 18:29.030
but...

18:29.270 --> 18:30.400
you were concerned?

18:34.710 --> 18:36.160
Concern for an employee?

18:37.160 --> 18:38.560
You could put it that way.

18:42.810 --> 18:43.850
Don't worry,

18:43.880 --> 18:45.080
I won't betray you.

18:46.100 --> 18:50.650
♪ Close your eyes for me ♪

18:52.180 --> 18:54.350
♪ Don't rush to wake up ♪

18:52.400 --> 18:53.270
Because...

18:53.680 --> 18:55.710
people who can stay by your side

18:54.820 --> 18:58.040
♪ Before the night ends ♪

18:58.160 --> 18:59.220
are all very smart.

18:59.640 --> 19:00.600
Since you brought it here,

19:00.600 --> 19:01.960
just let me keep it as a souvenir.

19:00.920 --> 19:06.240
♪ Will you stay with me? ♪

19:01.960 --> 19:03.690
You said you would give it to me.

19:07.160 --> 19:09.160
♪ I won't search for ♪

19:09.960 --> 19:12.770
♪ The reason we met ♪

19:10.640 --> 19:11.310
What's wrong with your hand?

19:11.310 --> 19:12.710
Is this hand hurting too?

19:14.510 --> 19:14.990
No.

19:14.550 --> 19:20.080
♪ The city gradually turns pale
outside the window ♪

19:15.510 --> 19:18.370
I just got scratched
while catching crabs earlier.

19:18.680 --> 19:19.840
I should have caught them for you.

19:19.840 --> 19:22.270
I do know how to steam crabs.

19:21.460 --> 19:23.580
♪ The stars twinkle ♪

19:24.570 --> 19:28.580
♪ I've quieted down ♪

19:25.550 --> 19:26.680
It's just a prop.

19:26.680 --> 19:27.960
You want to fight over this too?

19:27.960 --> 19:29.200
It's just a prop?

19:29.200 --> 19:31.680
You are already running such an impressive
murder mystery game shop.

19:30.310 --> 19:33.510
♪ What kind of story will you like? ♪

19:31.680 --> 19:32.610
How petty of you.

19:33.630 --> 19:35.290
♪ Would you join me? ♪

19:34.470 --> 19:35.440
Speaking of this,

19:35.320 --> 19:39.080
♪ To make a long, romantic dream ♪

19:35.710 --> 19:37.170
you don't seem surprised.

19:37.510 --> 19:39.070
I kind of guessed it.

19:39.710 --> 19:41.750
So the set designs in
the murder mystery game

19:39.800 --> 19:42.370
♪ Just you and me ♪

19:41.750 --> 19:43.550
were also created by you, right?

19:43.710 --> 19:44.400
Not bad.

19:44.400 --> 19:45.400
You've figured that out.

19:45.090 --> 19:47.270
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

19:45.710 --> 19:46.710
You've improved.

19:47.300 --> 19:49.280
♪ Carefully drawing close to you ♪

19:47.510 --> 19:48.400
Mr. Xiao,

19:48.710 --> 19:50.600
just how much else about you

19:49.310 --> 19:52.750
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

19:50.600 --> 19:52.030
do I still not know?

19:53.190 --> 19:56.880
♪ Oh, special night ♪

19:54.120 --> 19:55.600
What else do you want to know?

19:55.600 --> 19:56.660
About many things!

19:56.680 --> 19:57.410
For example,

19:57.620 --> 19:58.950
why do you play as an NPC?

19:59.310 --> 20:00.680
You said you're really busy with work.

19:59.940 --> 20:04.630
♪ I need you maybe ♪

20:00.680 --> 20:01.790
Moreover, unexpected incidents

20:01.790 --> 20:03.440
like today's could occur at any time.

20:03.440 --> 20:05.640
Why do you still squeeze in time to act?

20:05.920 --> 20:07.920
♪ The crowds are gone ♪

20:07.160 --> 20:07.790
Why did you

20:07.790 --> 20:09.360
start playing murder mystery games
in the first place?

20:08.600 --> 20:12.130
♪ My thoughts have sunk to the bottom ♪

20:10.840 --> 20:12.440
Because it's fun, of course.

20:12.840 --> 20:14.640
Once I enter Rongcheng,

20:14.250 --> 20:19.380
♪ Maybe you never noticed me at all ♪

20:14.640 --> 20:16.120
I'll forget all the troubles

20:16.120 --> 20:17.200
on the outside.

20:17.510 --> 20:18.920
I don't have to be myself.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.440
In reality,

20:21.090 --> 20:26.630
♪ Yet you're in my view ♪

20:21.440 --> 20:23.990
being myself rarely leads to victory.

20:24.440 --> 20:25.840
But in the game,

20:25.840 --> 20:27.310
I can occasionally experience

20:27.310 --> 20:28.470
what winning feels like.

20:28.240 --> 20:30.780
♪ Escape the world ♪

20:30.810 --> 20:32.810
♪ Forget all things ♪

20:32.830 --> 20:36.190
♪ And fall down a long, romantic dream ♪

20:33.310 --> 20:34.640
When I enter Rongcheng,

20:35.990 --> 20:37.550
I can also quit being Xiao Zhiyu.

20:36.210 --> 20:38.520
♪ Just you and me ♪

20:39.210 --> 20:41.530
♪ Under moonlight ♪

20:41.360 --> 20:43.840
You are not satisfied being Xiao Zhiyu?

20:43.840 --> 20:45.790
Who else do you want to be? Qin Xiaoyi?

20:43.890 --> 20:46.460
♪ Briefly, beyond the clamor ♪

20:46.500 --> 20:48.400
♪ Getting closer to you secretly ♪

20:48.420 --> 20:52.270
♪ Clinging to that trace of unknown joy ♪

20:52.660 --> 20:56.670
♪ Oh, special night ♪

20:59.900 --> 21:04.170
♪ We will meet tomorrow ♪

21:05.430 --> 21:07.040
♪ I know ♪

21:07.530 --> 21:11.390
♪ Oh, special night ♪

21:14.590 --> 21:18.600
♪ Oh, special night ♪

21:16.310 --> 21:18.070
Even the props are so detailed.

21:19.840 --> 21:21.770
No wonder the boss is an architect.

21:37.840 --> 21:40.120
You are not satisfied being Xiao Zhiyu?

21:40.380 --> 21:42.440
Who else do you want to be? Qin Xiaoyi?

21:53.470 --> 21:54.200
Xiaoyi.

21:54.470 --> 21:55.440
It's time for bed.

21:55.440 --> 21:56.120
Dad,

21:56.250 --> 21:57.510
can you just wait a little longer?

21:57.510 --> 21:58.950
I'm almost done drawing.

22:00.800 --> 22:02.680
Dad, look at the building I designed.

22:02.680 --> 22:04.280
It's even taller than yours.

22:05.550 --> 22:06.200
Xiaoyi,

22:06.520 --> 22:07.910
your drawing is wonderful.

22:07.910 --> 22:10.440
I want to turn it into
a real building someday.

22:11.230 --> 22:11.960
You will.

22:32.640 --> 22:33.990
So Qin Xiaoyi

22:34.230 --> 22:35.920
is a man of stories.

22:52.960 --> 22:53.680
Mr. Xiao,

22:54.390 --> 22:55.790
I brought you breakfast.

22:57.550 --> 22:58.150
Thank you.

23:04.990 --> 23:06.160
How's your hand?

23:07.200 --> 23:08.400
It doesn't hurt as much anymore,

23:08.400 --> 23:10.000
but it's still a bit swollen.

23:13.200 --> 23:14.070
What's this?

23:15.440 --> 23:17.600
I saw your fridge was almost empty,

23:17.670 --> 23:19.400
so I bought some instant meals.

23:20.120 --> 23:21.550
You just need to heat them up,

23:21.550 --> 23:23.480
so you don't have to cook yourself.

23:27.400 --> 23:28.270
Let me do it.

23:30.340 --> 23:33.400
I'm not completely incapable of
taking care of myself.

23:35.640 --> 23:36.160
Here.

23:37.470 --> 23:37.960
Take it.

23:39.510 --> 23:40.030
Thanks.

23:41.550 --> 23:42.200
Mr. Xiao,

23:42.400 --> 23:44.330
I can drive you to the office today.

23:45.820 --> 23:48.120
Isn't Xiao He on a business trip
with Ms. Zhou?

23:48.120 --> 23:50.720
I see your hands aren't
in a condition to drive.

24:14.310 --> 24:15.230
Looking at this background,

24:15.230 --> 24:17.960
it's that murder mystery game shop
in the industrial park?

24:17.960 --> 24:19.120
I heard there was a woman

24:19.120 --> 24:20.700
who cheated with an NPC from the shop,

24:20.700 --> 24:22.200
so the man in the video was very angry

24:22.200 --> 24:23.440
and wanted to catch the adulterer.

24:23.440 --> 24:25.680
I heard it was a love triangle.

24:25.680 --> 24:26.990
One of these women is the current partner,

24:26.990 --> 24:28.650
and the other is the mistress.

24:29.210 --> 24:30.080
Is that for real?

24:30.080 --> 24:30.950
That's scary.

24:30.980 --> 24:32.190
You should have seen

24:32.680 --> 24:34.070
that girl called Hu Xiu.

24:34.070 --> 24:36.120
She went straight up
and slapped that jerk.

24:36.120 --> 24:37.710
Although she's scared of ghosts,

24:37.710 --> 24:39.840
she sure isn't afraid to charge at people.

24:39.840 --> 24:42.310
The one who's in trouble should be
Qin Xiaoyi from Group A.

24:42.310 --> 24:42.990
I think

24:42.990 --> 24:45.510
we should call our Second Boss now.

24:46.660 --> 24:48.320
That statue was really heavy.

24:48.470 --> 24:50.870
His hand must be
at least slightly injured.

24:52.840 --> 24:54.100
Qin Xiaoyi is injured?

24:54.510 --> 24:56.230
But it shouldn't be too serious.

24:56.230 --> 24:56.790
Boss,

24:57.030 --> 24:59.290
have you seen the video in the group chat?

24:59.310 --> 25:00.110
I just saw it.

25:00.310 --> 25:02.440
The group is full of the park's regulars.

25:02.440 --> 25:03.750
If this spreads out,

25:03.750 --> 25:05.280
it would be terrible for us.

25:06.680 --> 25:07.270
How about

25:07.270 --> 25:09.160
we share the video of the Second Boss
saving someone

25:09.160 --> 25:09.750
instead?

25:09.750 --> 25:10.400
Nonsense.

25:12.270 --> 25:13.700
Remember this, all of you.

25:13.700 --> 25:15.980
Stop calling him "Second Boss"
from now on.

25:15.980 --> 25:17.870
Just treat him as Qin Xiaoyi.

25:18.270 --> 25:19.440
We'll be acting together again
in the future.

25:19.440 --> 25:21.370
Just be more natural, understand?

25:24.680 --> 25:25.120
Fei.

25:25.980 --> 25:27.710
Obtain the surveillance footage

25:27.710 --> 25:28.750
and show it to me.

25:31.710 --> 25:34.110
We are definitely not sharing it publicly.

25:34.310 --> 25:35.510
I'm just curious

25:36.270 --> 25:37.800
how he rescued that person.

25:38.160 --> 25:38.680
Okay.

25:44.160 --> 25:45.840
Hu Xiu and this girl

25:45.840 --> 25:48.230
went up and beat this guy together?

25:48.440 --> 25:49.640
They don't look like

25:49.640 --> 25:51.570
the current lover or the mistress.

25:52.160 --> 25:52.790
Mr. Gong.

25:53.440 --> 25:54.230
People in the group chat

25:54.230 --> 25:55.700
are just spreading rumors.

25:55.700 --> 25:56.360
This girl is

25:56.360 --> 25:56.790
Regard Café's

25:56.790 --> 25:57.600
Ms. Zhao.

25:57.600 --> 25:59.030
She's childhood friends with Hu Xiu.

25:59.030 --> 26:00.170
I know both of them.

26:00.550 --> 26:01.200
That Ms. Zhao,

26:01.200 --> 26:02.600
isn't she in the group chat?

26:02.600 --> 26:04.660
Why doesn't she come out and explain?

26:05.230 --> 26:05.920
Last night,

26:05.920 --> 26:06.920
many other players

26:06.920 --> 26:08.790
came to me complaining about
this Miyazaki guy,

26:08.790 --> 26:10.190
saying he has no manners.

26:10.230 --> 26:11.310
Why don't we help by

26:11.310 --> 26:12.520
saying something in the group chat?

26:12.520 --> 26:13.070
Wait a minute.

26:13.070 --> 26:13.550
Hold on.

26:13.840 --> 26:14.960
Since the people involved
haven't come forward,

26:14.960 --> 26:18.820
it's not appropriate for us to discuss
our client's private matters.

26:19.440 --> 26:20.700
He won't come forward.

26:21.380 --> 26:22.250
Why not?

26:22.960 --> 26:24.750
This guy is called Qian Jinxin.

26:24.990 --> 26:27.790
He's the new operations manager
of our industrial park.

26:27.790 --> 26:30.310
So many things happen in
Shanghai every day.

26:30.510 --> 26:32.690
Everyone's attention will shift quickly.

26:32.690 --> 26:34.680
I've got to save my dignity somehow,

26:34.680 --> 26:35.550
so that my little shop

26:35.550 --> 26:37.150
can continue to operate peacefully.

26:37.150 --> 26:38.680
Are we still asking for compensation?

26:38.680 --> 26:39.840
Ms. Zhao left her contact information

26:39.840 --> 26:41.260
and said to contact her when convenient.

26:41.260 --> 26:41.870
Forget it.

26:41.890 --> 26:43.230
It wasn't her fault anyway.

26:43.230 --> 26:44.070
Besides,

26:44.710 --> 26:45.640
she looks like someone

26:45.640 --> 26:47.030
you shouldn't mess with.

26:47.030 --> 26:48.400
Why should I cause trouble for myself

26:48.400 --> 26:50.060
over that little bit of money?

26:53.750 --> 26:54.710
It's no trouble.

26:55.220 --> 26:57.950
Mr. Gong, let's settle this
strictly by the book.

27:03.790 --> 27:04.460
Mr. Xiao,

27:05.230 --> 27:06.270
here's a document

27:06.270 --> 27:07.800
that needs your signature.

27:10.640 --> 27:10.990
Mr. Xiao,

27:10.990 --> 27:12.520
what happened to your hand?

27:12.910 --> 27:14.840
It's nothing. Just a minor injury.

27:18.270 --> 27:18.840
Mr. Xiao,

27:19.400 --> 27:19.750
your keys.

27:19.750 --> 27:20.840
Keep it with you for now.

27:20.840 --> 27:24.040
Until He returns, you're in charge of
ferrying me around.

27:25.990 --> 27:26.850
Anything else?

27:27.590 --> 27:28.390
No.

27:42.070 --> 27:43.660
Hu Xiu, you bought a car?

27:45.310 --> 27:45.830
No.

27:45.860 --> 27:47.530
I found a part-time job

27:48.000 --> 27:49.130
as a private driver.

27:49.600 --> 27:49.920
Well then,

27:49.920 --> 27:51.120
be careful out there.

27:58.920 --> 27:59.400
Zhao,

27:59.400 --> 28:00.440
where are you?

28:00.880 --> 28:02.810
Why did you close the shop so early?

28:02.880 --> 28:04.160
Xiu, I'm at home.

28:04.640 --> 28:06.270
Isn't Guangming on a business trip?

28:06.270 --> 28:07.800
Why did you go home so early?

28:08.200 --> 28:08.680
I even

28:08.680 --> 28:10.120
brought you your favorite late-night snack

28:10.120 --> 28:11.520
so we could eat together.

28:11.790 --> 28:13.450
Business was just okay today.

28:13.940 --> 28:15.540
I just wanted to take it easy.

28:15.550 --> 28:16.160
Alright.

28:16.160 --> 28:17.510
Get some rest then.

28:23.680 --> 28:24.600
Zhao, I've got something to do.

28:24.600 --> 28:25.530
I'll hang up now.

28:29.020 --> 28:30.820
Aren't you going to invite me in?

28:34.120 --> 28:35.030
Mr. Qian.

28:35.460 --> 28:37.660
please speak your mind.

28:38.070 --> 28:39.640
With you stomping all over the place,

28:39.640 --> 28:40.310
the floor will get dirty,

28:40.310 --> 28:41.900
and I'll have to mop it again.

28:41.900 --> 28:43.160
Ms. Hu, I heard that you

28:43.160 --> 28:44.290
live just upstairs.

28:44.980 --> 28:45.980
Who told you that?

28:47.510 --> 28:49.370
I happened to pass by a few days ago

28:49.680 --> 28:51.410
and saw the lights on upstairs.

28:52.360 --> 28:52.920
So I

28:52.920 --> 28:55.980
checked the industrial park's
entry and exit records.

28:57.390 --> 28:58.470
Yes, I live here.

28:58.490 --> 28:59.900
This is my friend's shop.

28:59.960 --> 29:01.550
She signed a contract with
the industrial park

29:01.550 --> 29:03.010
and had already paid rent.

29:03.030 --> 29:04.360
I'm just staying here temporarily.

29:04.360 --> 29:05.470
Is there a problem?

29:05.710 --> 29:08.030
Tenants cannot use commercial spaces
as residences.

29:08.030 --> 29:09.550
That's the industrial park's policy.

29:09.550 --> 29:11.420
Ms. Hu, up until today,

29:11.880 --> 29:14.470
you've been living here for
almost two months, right?

29:14.470 --> 29:16.760
If it were just two or three days,

29:16.780 --> 29:18.310
I could pretend not to know.

29:19.510 --> 29:20.920
But two months...

29:21.750 --> 29:23.610
that's a bit difficult to ignore.

29:25.230 --> 29:26.160
What do you want?

29:28.370 --> 29:30.160
I'm responsible for managing
this industrial park.

29:30.160 --> 29:32.110
I can't just know about it and
not report it, right?

29:32.110 --> 29:34.030
But if I report this...

29:34.640 --> 29:35.960
your friend's shop

29:36.780 --> 29:38.710
might be shut down for violations.

29:39.070 --> 29:39.840
However,

29:40.470 --> 29:42.880
rules are rigid, but we can be flexible.

29:42.880 --> 29:45.080
Since you now understand your mistake,

29:45.360 --> 29:47.510
if you just join me for dinner and drinks

29:47.510 --> 29:48.640
and apologize,

29:49.260 --> 29:50.350
perhaps I

29:50.370 --> 29:52.570
could turn a blind eye to this.

29:53.470 --> 29:54.160
No need.

29:54.880 --> 29:56.620
I'll move out as soon as possible.

29:56.620 --> 29:58.150
Please leave immediately.

30:01.490 --> 30:03.890
If you don't leave,
I'm calling the police.

30:17.970 --> 30:18.630
No problem.

30:18.640 --> 30:20.300
Let's proceed with this plan.

30:20.720 --> 30:22.600
The second draft was well coordinated.

30:22.600 --> 30:23.270
Now, the proposal

30:23.270 --> 30:24.610
is in its final stages of revision.

30:24.610 --> 30:26.140
We can't let our guard down.

30:30.510 --> 30:31.840
Is there anything else?

30:32.390 --> 30:33.030
Mr. Xiao,

30:33.920 --> 30:35.470
you just said

30:35.790 --> 30:37.160
this plan is now

30:37.160 --> 30:38.960
in its final stages of revision.

30:38.990 --> 30:40.400
Doesn't that mean many things

30:40.400 --> 30:42.160
have already been settled?

30:42.550 --> 30:44.470
So we might not need some...

30:44.920 --> 30:46.780
external inspiration to fuel it.

30:47.680 --> 30:49.280
Just say what's on your mind.

30:51.030 --> 30:52.160
Back then,

30:52.160 --> 30:53.960
didn't you move into the lane in search of

30:53.960 --> 30:55.690
inspiration for this project?

30:56.360 --> 30:57.920
So since this project

30:57.920 --> 30:59.600
is coming to an end now,

31:00.360 --> 31:03.080
isn't it about time you moved out?

31:04.740 --> 31:06.160
It hasn't been three months yet.

31:06.160 --> 31:06.980
According to the contract,

31:06.980 --> 31:08.700
I can stay as long as I want.

31:11.070 --> 31:13.600
Then can I move in and
share the place with you?

31:17.740 --> 31:20.200
I have to drive you
to and from work every day,

31:20.360 --> 31:22.290
which has doubled my commute time.

31:22.440 --> 31:23.510
You know very well

31:23.510 --> 31:24.840
how my hand got injured.

31:25.630 --> 31:27.550
Of course I know, Mr. Xiao.

31:28.630 --> 31:30.930
It's my responsibility to drive you
to and from work.

31:30.930 --> 31:32.130
I'm not running away.

31:32.750 --> 31:33.990
I'm just wondering if we could

31:33.990 --> 31:35.160
make things

31:35.250 --> 31:36.070
a little easier.

31:36.070 --> 31:36.750
No.

31:41.390 --> 31:42.080
Mr. Xiao,

31:42.100 --> 31:42.650
goodbye.

31:54.910 --> 31:55.970
What are you doing?

31:56.920 --> 31:57.600
As you all know,

31:57.600 --> 31:59.470
we once developed
a social media application

31:58.610 --> 32:01.550
[Software Innovation and Development
Technical Exchange Conference]

31:59.470 --> 32:02.400
which generated quite a bit of discussion.

32:02.680 --> 32:03.270
Well,

32:03.550 --> 32:05.840
the chain of trust issue in
anonymous social networking

32:05.840 --> 32:08.640
is sometimes like
the Byzantine Generals Problem.

32:08.640 --> 32:10.640
Users need to hide their identities

32:10.640 --> 32:12.480
while also establishing connections.

32:12.480 --> 32:13.240
Therefore,

32:13.310 --> 32:15.310
in this iteration we've introduced

32:15.310 --> 32:17.750
the concept of reinforcement learning
with weak ties.

32:17.750 --> 32:19.880
Let's explore this concept together.

32:24.660 --> 32:25.390
Guangming!

32:26.510 --> 32:27.160
Cheng Han.

32:29.160 --> 32:30.490
What are you doing here?

32:31.550 --> 32:32.550
What have you been up to
these past two years?

32:32.550 --> 32:33.960
We haven't heard anything from you.

32:33.960 --> 32:35.100
I'm just getting by.

32:35.160 --> 32:36.360
You're being modest again.

32:36.360 --> 32:37.200
I heard your

32:37.200 --> 32:38.930
entire presentation just now.

32:39.380 --> 32:40.100
So,

32:40.160 --> 32:41.600
when should we organize a class reunion?

32:41.600 --> 32:42.880
I haven't seen you for just two years,

32:42.880 --> 32:43.760
and it feels like

32:43.760 --> 32:45.220
we've grown a bit distant.

32:45.230 --> 32:45.710
Sure.

32:46.400 --> 32:46.840
By then, let's...

32:46.840 --> 32:47.600
Cheng Han.

32:50.110 --> 32:50.790
Senior.

32:53.100 --> 32:54.250
This is Chi Xin.

32:54.270 --> 32:56.040
She was in the same major as us
in college.

32:56.040 --> 32:58.910
I remember she was two years behind us,

32:58.950 --> 33:00.880
and now she's working at Zhiteng.

33:02.790 --> 33:03.600
Chi Xin?

33:04.820 --> 33:05.650
My fault.

33:06.050 --> 33:07.920
We took some general courses together,

33:07.920 --> 33:08.270
didn't we?

33:08.270 --> 33:08.750
Yes.

33:09.120 --> 33:09.790
It's been 7 years

33:09.790 --> 33:11.920
since we last met,
which was at your graduation.

33:11.920 --> 33:13.720
It's normal not to recognize me.

33:13.790 --> 33:15.440
Actually, you've become more beautiful,

33:15.440 --> 33:16.310
so it's no wonder

33:16.310 --> 33:17.030
we didn't recognize you.

33:17.030 --> 33:18.120
Senior, since we're from the same major,

33:18.120 --> 33:19.920
how about exchanging contacts?

33:22.700 --> 33:23.700
It's my wife.

33:23.990 --> 33:24.790
My wife's calling.

33:24.790 --> 33:26.120
You should take it then.

33:28.070 --> 33:28.550
Hi, honey.

33:28.550 --> 33:30.010
So, you are at Zhiteng now?

33:30.600 --> 33:32.030
I've been revising my speech

33:32.030 --> 33:33.550
from last night until this morning.

33:33.550 --> 33:34.510
Then, I just had to deal with

33:34.510 --> 33:36.020
a bunch of miscellaneous tasks,

33:36.020 --> 33:37.930
so I didn't have time to check my phone.

33:37.930 --> 33:38.530
By the way,

33:38.660 --> 33:40.310
I met two college classmates today.

33:40.310 --> 33:41.750
One you know, Cheng Han,

33:41.750 --> 33:43.210
my college roommate,

33:43.360 --> 33:44.580
and a junior female classmate

33:44.580 --> 33:46.580
who seems to be doing quite well now.

33:47.680 --> 33:49.680
It was quite a coincidence, anyway.

33:50.810 --> 33:51.370
Mr. Xiao,

33:51.640 --> 33:52.270
I thought

33:52.270 --> 33:54.190
it would be Mr. Gong signing it today.

33:54.190 --> 33:55.990
He had something urgent come up.

33:56.750 --> 33:58.470
Previously, I mentioned to Mr. Gong that

33:58.470 --> 33:59.360
the industrial park wants to

33:59.360 --> 34:01.080
collaborate with the club
on some marketing events.

34:01.080 --> 34:02.710
So when the proposal is ready,

34:02.710 --> 34:03.820
I'll send it to you.

34:03.850 --> 34:05.840
Just give it directly to Gong Huaicong.

34:05.840 --> 34:07.230
Okay, that works.

34:07.880 --> 34:09.070
No, let me treat you.

34:09.070 --> 34:10.150
It's okay, let me have it.

34:10.150 --> 34:10.670
No,

34:10.800 --> 34:11.469
Mr. Xiao,

34:11.469 --> 34:12.110
you see,

34:12.110 --> 34:14.670
our industrial park values the cooperation
with your club.

34:14.670 --> 34:16.360
Since you're willing to renew
for another two years,

34:16.360 --> 34:17.440
it's only fair

34:17.440 --> 34:18.770
that I should treat you.

34:18.840 --> 34:20.760
If the club has any needs in the future,

34:20.760 --> 34:21.690
just let us know.

34:23.239 --> 34:23.770
Alright.

34:23.900 --> 34:24.580
Hello,

34:24.600 --> 34:26.000
two Americanos, please.

34:32.880 --> 34:33.719
Mr. Xiao,

34:34.190 --> 34:36.080
the club must have quite a few employees.

34:36.080 --> 34:38.340
They don't live on the premises, do they?

34:38.350 --> 34:38.830
No,

34:38.980 --> 34:41.110
we've arranged dormitories for them.

34:41.179 --> 34:42.130
That's good.

34:42.550 --> 34:44.010
Is there something wrong?

34:44.139 --> 34:44.909
Nothing.

34:44.929 --> 34:46.590
It's good that you don't have that issue.

34:46.590 --> 34:48.190
How's it going? Is the coffee ready?

34:48.190 --> 34:48.790
Yes, it is.

34:54.070 --> 34:54.630
Ms. Hu,

34:55.070 --> 34:55.760
there are some things

34:55.760 --> 34:57.240
I need to tell you in advance.

34:57.240 --> 34:58.590
There are actually quite a few
residential complexes

34:58.590 --> 34:59.760
near our lane.

34:59.760 --> 35:01.550
But the budget you've given

35:01.550 --> 35:02.960
is truly on the low side.

35:03.880 --> 35:04.760
Moreover,

35:04.780 --> 35:06.250
since it's for a one-month
short-term rental,

35:06.250 --> 35:06.910
it's even harder

35:06.910 --> 35:08.570
to negotiate with this price.

35:08.960 --> 35:10.800
I'm aware of all the issues you mentioned,

35:10.800 --> 35:12.110
but I'd still appreciate

35:12.110 --> 35:13.760
if you could keep an eye out for me.

35:13.760 --> 35:14.840
Sure, sure.

35:18.960 --> 35:21.400
That Mr. Xiao who rented
your previous place,

35:21.400 --> 35:22.800
is he still living there?

35:23.190 --> 35:24.640
It's precisely because
he's still renting it

35:24.640 --> 35:26.500
that I need to find another place.

35:27.920 --> 35:30.030
This Mr. Xiao is also quite strange.

35:30.030 --> 35:31.240
I previously introduced him to

35:31.240 --> 35:32.710
that new complex nearby.

35:32.990 --> 35:34.440
It even has free parking spaces

35:34.440 --> 35:35.500
available for him.

35:35.680 --> 35:37.200
But he wasn't interested

35:37.220 --> 35:39.240
and insisted on living in some old lane.

35:39.240 --> 35:40.190
At first, he even said

35:40.190 --> 35:41.550
he must find something

35:42.020 --> 35:43.670
near Lane 7, Number 11.

35:44.470 --> 35:45.800
Lane 7, Number 11?

35:46.190 --> 35:47.590
Isn't that place vacant?

35:47.720 --> 35:48.470
He's not short of money,

35:48.470 --> 35:50.030
so why didn't he just rent
that place directly?

35:50.030 --> 35:51.960
That house isn't available for rent.

35:51.960 --> 35:54.560
The owner bought it for
the sake of collecting.

35:55.960 --> 35:58.240
I've heard of property investment,

35:58.630 --> 35:59.760
but for collection?

36:00.610 --> 36:02.530
That landlord is really wealthy.

36:03.150 --> 36:03.840
He even has

36:04.150 --> 36:06.080
his own Baidu encyclopedia entry.

36:13.240 --> 36:14.030
This Xie Lin

36:14.030 --> 36:15.960
used to live on Yanhua Road
when he was a child.

36:15.960 --> 36:16.470
Since childhood,

36:16.470 --> 36:17.440
he grew up in this lane

36:17.440 --> 36:18.880
with his grandfather.

36:19.110 --> 36:19.760
Unfortunately,

36:19.760 --> 36:21.280
when he was in his teens,

36:21.280 --> 36:22.730
his grandfather passed away.

36:22.730 --> 36:25.190
He had to go live with his parents
in Shenzhen,

36:25.190 --> 36:26.790
and later went abroad.

36:26.840 --> 36:27.550
This house

36:27.550 --> 36:29.370
changed hands many times.

36:29.550 --> 36:30.150
In the end,

36:30.150 --> 36:31.590
it was my mentor who made the connection

36:31.590 --> 36:33.320
and helped buy it back.

36:34.260 --> 36:35.340
That makes sense.

36:35.940 --> 36:38.160
No wonder he insisted on living
in this lane.

36:38.160 --> 36:39.930
It was for Xie Lin all along.

36:39.960 --> 36:40.920
So that means we have to wait until

36:40.920 --> 36:42.320
the design competition is over

36:42.320 --> 36:43.150
before moving out?

36:43.150 --> 36:43.610
Well...

36:44.360 --> 36:47.030
I'll just have to share the place
with him then.

36:48.010 --> 36:49.740
Share?

36:54.570 --> 36:55.340
Ms. Zhou?

36:55.890 --> 36:56.600
Hu Xiu,

36:56.630 --> 36:57.940
check the message I sent you.

36:57.940 --> 37:00.070
Send me a copy of all the materials
mentioned there.

37:00.070 --> 37:00.920
I'm sorry, Ms. Zhou.

37:00.920 --> 37:01.550
I wasn't

37:01.550 --> 37:03.350
looking at my messages just now.

37:04.570 --> 37:05.670
I'll send them to you.

37:05.670 --> 37:06.470
Just a moment.

37:07.400 --> 37:07.920
It's already late.

37:07.920 --> 37:09.470
I'm sorry for disturbing you.

37:09.470 --> 37:10.630
I had no choice either.

37:10.630 --> 37:13.080
I just received a notification from Lyman
earlier tonight that

37:13.080 --> 37:15.280
the submission deadline has suddenly been
moved up by two days.

37:15.280 --> 37:15.840
So I thought

37:15.840 --> 37:17.420
I should quickly confirm these materials.

37:17.420 --> 37:17.990
Tomorrow morning,

37:17.990 --> 37:19.030
I will work with the team to...

37:19.030 --> 37:20.510
Early submission?

37:38.830 --> 37:39.540
Mr. Xiao,

37:39.920 --> 37:42.070
what happened to your hand?

37:42.550 --> 37:44.280
You received the email, right?

37:44.490 --> 37:46.110
The submission deadline has been moved up.

37:46.110 --> 37:48.110
I'm worried about our progress now.

37:48.230 --> 37:49.800
Can you still draw with your hand?

37:49.800 --> 37:50.800
It's not serious.

37:51.070 --> 37:52.400
After a few more days of recovery,

37:52.400 --> 37:54.600
I'll speed up and get the drawings done.

37:55.190 --> 37:56.400
You should rest properly first.

37:56.400 --> 37:57.540
Don't force yourself to work.

37:57.540 --> 37:59.400
Your hand's recovery is very important.

37:59.400 --> 38:00.510
I'll see if I can

38:00.510 --> 38:01.760
transfer a designer from

38:01.760 --> 38:03.400
another project to assist you.

38:03.400 --> 38:04.070
Got it.

38:11.110 --> 38:11.760
Mr. Xiao.

38:14.030 --> 38:14.590
Come in.

38:19.320 --> 38:21.150
After hearing the revised proposal,

38:21.150 --> 38:23.030
I tried to draw
some revised designs myself.

38:23.030 --> 38:25.210
Would you mind taking a look?

38:36.440 --> 38:37.370
Mr. Xiao.

38:37.400 --> 38:39.000
I've been thinking all night

38:39.280 --> 38:41.830
about how I can
better fulfill my responsibilities.

38:41.830 --> 38:43.870
Since your hand is injured

38:43.890 --> 38:46.410
and these revisions are urgent,

38:46.720 --> 38:47.760
if you have any work

38:47.760 --> 38:49.450
that I can help with,

38:49.480 --> 38:51.340
please don't hesitate to tell me.

38:51.630 --> 38:52.400
How did you know

38:52.400 --> 38:54.440
the revisions are urgent?

38:55.470 --> 38:55.960
Well...

38:56.360 --> 38:59.240
time was already tight to begin with.

39:02.560 --> 39:03.640
So I think

39:04.190 --> 39:05.280
you should reconsider

39:05.280 --> 39:07.740
my suggestion about sharing the apartment.

39:09.570 --> 39:11.370
I can help you with the drawings.

39:11.530 --> 39:13.660
Working overtime is no problem at all.

39:14.400 --> 39:15.660
While you're injured,

39:15.880 --> 39:16.920
I'll take care of all the housework.

39:16.920 --> 39:17.670
In short,

39:17.670 --> 39:20.320
I can completely become
your new right hand.

39:25.310 --> 39:27.710
You really want to be roommates
that badly?

39:29.280 --> 39:32.470
The café cannot possibly be
as comfortable as home.

39:32.470 --> 39:33.190
And your work efficiency

39:33.190 --> 39:35.150
won't be as high as when you're at home.

39:35.150 --> 39:37.030
Whether from a personal perspective,

39:37.030 --> 39:38.550
or from a work perspective,

39:38.550 --> 39:40.550
or from your perspective, Mr. Xiao,

39:40.800 --> 39:43.110
sharing an apartment is a great choice.

39:49.440 --> 39:49.920
Fine.

39:50.250 --> 39:51.470
Move back as soon as possible.

39:51.470 --> 39:52.870
We have a lot of work to do.

39:56.670 --> 39:57.880
Just like that?

39:58.860 --> 39:59.740
What else?

40:10.280 --> 40:10.960
Coming.

40:17.230 --> 40:18.160
Why are you here?

40:18.670 --> 40:20.070
I heard you hurt your hand.

40:20.070 --> 40:21.270
I came to check on you.

40:21.360 --> 40:22.150
Are you okay?

40:22.840 --> 40:23.640
It's nothing.

40:24.720 --> 40:25.800
You...

40:25.800 --> 40:27.200
You're so tight-lipped.

40:27.390 --> 40:29.390
Not a single word about your injury.

40:29.960 --> 40:32.690
I couldn't hide it from you
even if I tried my best.

40:32.710 --> 40:34.360
Why are you hiding

40:34.360 --> 40:35.890
this heroic rescue from me?

40:36.110 --> 40:37.070
You're sweating so much,

40:37.070 --> 40:37.960
yet still talking non-stop.

40:37.960 --> 40:39.360
Drink this to rehydrate.

40:40.150 --> 40:40.720
Oh right,

40:40.720 --> 40:41.400
try this

40:41.400 --> 40:42.030
medicinal patch later.

40:42.030 --> 40:43.230
I heard it works well.

40:46.280 --> 40:46.880
By the way,

40:48.260 --> 40:49.590
if you don't have anything important,

40:49.590 --> 40:51.030
stop coming over so often.

40:51.030 --> 40:52.560
Just giving you a heads-up.

40:53.240 --> 40:53.960
Why?

40:54.800 --> 40:56.330
The landlord moved back in.

40:57.980 --> 40:59.190
So are you moving out?

40:59.240 --> 41:00.240
Your hand is still injured.

41:00.240 --> 41:01.320
How can you move now?

41:01.320 --> 41:02.190
I'm not moving.

41:02.720 --> 41:03.580
We're sharing.

41:08.220 --> 41:09.220
Sharing?

41:11.040 --> 41:11.880
I'm really

41:11.880 --> 41:14.440
seeing Hu Xiu in a new light.

41:15.400 --> 41:15.990
No wonder

41:15.990 --> 41:18.990
someone started buying
grapefruit-flavored water.

41:19.520 --> 41:22.250
It's pretty impressive that she managed
to convince you

41:22.250 --> 41:23.510
to share an apartment.

41:24.150 --> 41:25.190
Could she be

41:25.190 --> 41:27.280
coming back just to repay you?

41:28.590 --> 41:31.120
She actually put on quite a show in front of me.

41:35.510 --> 41:36.670
Has her friend's café

41:36.670 --> 41:38.070
had any problems lately?

41:39.670 --> 41:41.130
It's operating normally.

41:41.550 --> 41:42.280
However,

41:42.760 --> 41:44.030
that video of them disciplining someone

41:44.030 --> 41:45.240
during the murder mystery game

41:45.240 --> 41:46.680
has spread throughout the industrial park.

41:46.680 --> 41:48.280
It must have had some impact.

41:49.050 --> 41:50.260
Go check for me

41:50.280 --> 41:51.550
if anything else has happened.
